<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="creator-hero">
  <div class="creator-hero__backdrop"></div>
  <img class="creator-mascot creator-mascot--hero-left" src="/characters/Untitled%20design%20(3).png" alt="" />
  <img class="creator-mascot creator-mascot--hero-right" src="/characters/Untitled%20design%20(5).png" alt="" />
  <div class="creator-hero__content">
    <div class="creator-hero__copy">
      <h1>Squig Creator portal</h1>
      <p class="creator-hero__tagline">Where chaos becomes canon.</p>
      <p class="lead">
        The Squig Creator Portal is where community creations become part of Squig Survival
        &mdash; the live Discord game where player-submitted art can appear as real moments,
        outcomes, revives, failures, and event scenes inside the game itself.
      </p>
      <p class="lead creator-hero__support">
        Your creations do not just sit in a gallery.<br />
        They get used.
      </p>
      <div class="actions creator-hero__actions">
        <% if (!user) { %>
          <a class="button" href="/auth/discord">Login with Discord</a>
        <% } else if (user.isGuildMember) { %>
          <a class="button" href="/submit">Open Submission Form</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a class="button" href="https://squigs.io/discord" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Ugly Labs Discord</a>
        <% } %>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://bueno.art/squigs/mint" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Mint a Squig</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="#how-it-works">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
      <div class="creator-hero__microcopy">
        Discord access is available from the link icon above.
      </div>
      <div class="creator-hero__meta">
        <span>Automatic rewards for connected creators</span>
        <span>Any NFT collection accepted</span>
        <span>Higher rewards for Squigs</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="creator-sidecard">
      <% if (!user) { %>
        <h2>Submit into the live game pool</h2>
        <p class="muted">
          Sign in with Discord, submit your image, and the team will review it for quality, creativity, and fit.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="button" href="/auth/discord">Login with Discord</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="https://bueno.art/squigs/mint" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Mint a Squig</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="https://squigs.io/discord" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <h2><%= user.isGuildMember ? "You are ready to create." : "Join the ecosystem to submit." %></h2>
        <div class="creator-status">
          <p><strong>Account:</strong> <%= user.username %></p>
          <p><strong>Membership:</strong> <%= user.isGuildMember ? "Verified" : "Not verified" %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <% if (user.isGuildMember) { %>
            <a class="button" href="/submit">Go to submission form</a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a class="button" href="https://squigs.io/discord" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join the Discord server</a>
          <% } %>
          <a class="button secondary" href="https://bueno.art/squigs/mint" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Mint a Squig</a>
          <% if (isAdmin) { %>
            <a class="button secondary" href="/admin">Open admin review</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="creator-section creator-section--intro">
  <div class="creator-section__heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">What Is This?</p>
    <h2>The submission system behind live Squig Survival moments.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="creator-copy">
    <p>
      The Squig Creator Portal is a community-powered submission system built for Squig Survival.
    </p>
    <p>
      Creators can submit images based on specific eras, outcomes, and game moments. Once approved, those
      creations are added directly into the live game pool, where they can appear during gameplay inside
      the Ugly Labs Discord.
    </p>
    <p>
      This means your art becomes part of the game experience itself &mdash; not just something people look
      at, but something players encounter live while playing.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="creator-section" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="creator-section__heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">How It Works</p>
    <h2>Simple submission flow, direct in-game impact.</h2>
  </div>
  <ol class="creator-steps">
    <li>Connect with Discord and submit your creation.</li>
    <li>Choose the era or game moment your image is meant for.</li>
    <li>Optionally include your prompt to help inspire other creators.</li>
    <li>Our team reviews submissions for quality, creativity, and fit.</li>
    <li>Approved creations are added into the Squig Survival game pool.</li>
    <li>When your image appears in a live game, it becomes part of the action.</li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section class="creator-section creator-section--rewards-wrap">
  <img class="creator-mascot creator-mascot--reward-left" src="/characters/Untitled%20design%20(1).png" alt="" />
  <img class="creator-mascot creator-mascot--reward-right" src="/characters/Untitled%20design%20(4).png" alt="" />
  <div class="creator-section__heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Rewards</p>
    <h2>Clear rates. Automatic creator rewards.</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      Creators are rewarded automatically when their approved creations are used in Squig Survival, as long
      as they are properly connected in the Ugly Labs Discord ecosystem.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="creator-rewards">
    <article class="panel creator-reward creator-reward--featured">
      <p class="creator-reward__label">Squigs creations</p>
      <p class="creator-reward__amount">150 <span>$CHARM</span></p>
      <p class="muted">Highest reward tier for creations built from the Squigs collection.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel creator-reward">
      <p class="creator-reward__label">Other collections</p>
      <p class="creator-reward__amount">100 <span>$CHARM</span></p>
      <p class="muted">Open to any NFT collection, with a solid baseline reward for approved work.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="creator-section">
  <div class="creator-section__heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Where Your Creations Appear</p>
    <h2>Used across the live game, not parked in a gallery.</h2>
  </div>
  <ul class="creator-tags">
    <li>survival events</li>
    <li>eliminations</li>
    <li>milestones</li>
    <li>lore moments</li>
    <li>!revive Success</li>
    <li>!revive Failed</li>
  </ul>
  <article class="creator-callout">
    These are not static gallery uploads. They are active parts of the game.
  </article>
</section>

<section class="creator-section">
  <div class="creator-section__heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Why It Matters</p>
    <h2>Community creativity actively expands the game world.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="creator-copy">
    <p>Squig Survival is not just a game people play. It is something the community helps build.</p>
    <p>
      Every approved creation expands the world, adds more variety to the experience, and gives creators a real
      way to contribute to the game while being rewarded for it.
    </p>
    <p>
      The result is a system where creativity, gameplay, and community all feed into each other.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="creator-cta">
  <div class="creator-section__heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Final CTA</p>
    <h2>Ready to create something weird, cinematic, chaotic, or unforgettable?</h2>
  </div>
  <p class="lead">
    Submit your creation, get it approved, watch it appear in-game, and earn rewards when it gets used.
  </p>
  <p class="lead creator-cta__closing">
    The portal is open.<br />
    The game is live.<br />
    And the Squigs are watching.
  </p>
  <div class="actions">
    <% if (!user) { %>
      <a class="button" href="/auth/discord">Login with Discord</a>
    <% } else if (user.isGuildMember) { %>
      <a class="button" href="/submit">Submit Your Creation</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a class="button" href="https://squigs.io/discord" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Ugly Labs Discord</a>
    <% } %>
    <a class="button secondary" href="https://bueno.art/squigs/mint" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Mint a Squig</a>
    <a class="button secondary" href="https://squigs.io/discord" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open Discord</a>
  </div>
  <div class="creator-cast" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="creator-cast__item creator-cast__item--tilt-left" src="/characters/Untitled%20design%20(2).png" alt="" />
    <img class="creator-cast__item" src="/characters/Untitled%20design%20(6).png" alt="" />
    <img class="creator-cast__item creator-cast__item--tilt-right" src="/characters/Untitled%20design%20(7).png" alt="" />
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>
